  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The registry enroll all the patients who suffered an out-of-hospital cardiac arrest in the
      Province of Pavia with a follow-up up to five years after the event.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The registry is an observational study which enroll all the patients who suffered an
      out-of-hospital cardiac arrest of any etiology in the Province of Pavia.

      The follow-up of the patients is at 1 month after the event, 6 month and every year up to
      five years after the event.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
